This is necessary because the tool doesn't now anything about the URL to reach it. This is only known by Q Server through toolEndpointConfig.
The tool just gives a name for scripts/stylesheets accessible from the endpoints /script/{name} and /stylesheet/{name}

Could also be a Script running in a Browser
